For HTML part:

Insert the class "item" before the image. Then the "caption" class.

e.g.

<span class="item" ><img src=""/></span>

<div or span class="">

<h2>Lorem Ipsum</h2>

<p>Lorem Ipsum</p>
</div or span>

for css

For personal styling edit 

.hover-grid .hover-grid-item
width, height

.hover-grid-item .caption

width, height 

For me I have set to width: auto and height: auto
